OL,3,C'Deep sadness': CMAT says her success
OL,4,Cis being tarnished by body shaming
OL,6,FIrish singer-songwriter CMAT has taken
OL,7,Fto social media to express her "deep
OL,8,Fsadness", saying she feels her growing
OL,9,Fsuccess is being "tarnished" by
OL,10,Fongoing body shaming.
OL,12,FCiara Mary-Alice Thompson, who goes by
OL,13,Fher initials CMAT, posted on Instagram
OL,14,Fafter feeling "compelled" to speak out
OL,15,Fafter a "difficult" few days.
OL,17,FThe star performed on the main stage
OL,18,Fof BBC Radio 1 Big Weekend in
OL,19,FSunderland on Sunday evening, and
OL,20,Flater received abuse via social media
OL,21,Fin relation to her weight.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
