OL,3,C'Deep sadness': CMAT says her success
OL,4,Cis being tarnished by body shaming
OL,6,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,F"It is literally so boring for me, a
OL,12,Fgorgeous genius, to keep having to yap
OL,13,Fon about how horribly I am treated
OL,14,Fbecause of my body," she wrote to her
OL,15,F350,000 followers on Thursday.
OL,17,FThe 30-year-old went on to say that
OL,18,Fshe would "love to stop" responding to
OL,19,Fthe abuse but that it "keeps happening
OL,20,Fat an accelerating and worsening pace"
OL,21,Fas her fame grows.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
