OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1780067467
OL,3,C'Deep sadness': CMAT says her success
OL,4,Cis being tarnished by body shaming
OL,6,F"There is no relief from this," she
OL,7,Fadded.
OL,9,FThe star also said that she was not
OL,10,F"being defiant" or choosing her weight
OL,11,Fas a "punk rock act of liberty".
OL,13,F"I simply have a body, one that I
OL,14,Fwould of course like to change in
OL,15,Forder to fit in and avoid all of this
OL,16,Fabuse, but I have had extreme
OL,17,Fdifficulty in doing so," she said.
OL,19,F"I don't get a say in whether or not I
OL,20,Fwant to be brave, I simply have to sit
OL,21,Fhere and take it."
OL,26,@{D@AOU}D@RO]
