OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1780067467
OL,3,C'Deep sadness': CMAT says her success
OL,4,Cis being tarnished by body shaming
OL,6,FDespite facing ongoing abuse regarding
OL,7,Fher body, the singer said she was
OL,8,Fstill "very happy and grateful" for
OL,9,Fher job and success.
OL,11,F"The feeling of seeing all your dreams
OL,12,Fcome true after so many years of
OL,13,Fconstant grinding towards them...
OL,14,Fchefs kiss," she wrote.
OL,16,F"But the success is increasingly
OL,17,Fbecoming tarnished by the fact that I
OL,18,Fwould be allowed to enjoy it so much
OL,19,Fmore if I was thin."
OL,26,@pD@GOUpD@_O]{D@TO]
