OL,3,C'Deep sadness': CMAT says her success
OL,4,Cis being tarnished by body shaming
OL,6,FCMAT has previously experienced body-
OL,7,Fshaming, and as she addressed this on
OL,8,Fstage at the festival last weekend,
OL,9,Fshe was met with support from the
OL,10,Faudience.
OL,12,FThe singer has also referenced the
OL,13,Fissue in her music, releasing her
OL,14,Fsingle Take a Sexy Picture of Me last
OL,15,Fyear, in which she speaks about the
OL,16,Fextreme beauty standards women face.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
